data.description: Fireplace for the cold. Pool for the heat. This Treat of a Retreat will be hard to beat! Well Maintained home with inground pool and tons of charm. Carpet-free living at its finest! Living room boasts a fireplace and bonus office/den/sunroom which has barn door for additional privacy. Storage for days in the dining room. Plenty of room for a pantry or memento display. Master suite has RARE Walk-In TUB along and 2 separate vanities and walk-in closets. Lots of extra storage throughout home. Wait until you see the backyard! Bonus covered patio bask poolside. Besides the inground pool, there's ample room for a garden or shop. Property backs up to Bryant. New Roof Jan. 3, 2024.
